- Tested on Windows 10 desktop.
#### New observations;

I noticed that when using a 8x8 pixmap it in fact produces a horizontal black _rectangle_. (4x8 I think). I said square earlier, this was wrong.
The rectangle might imply the fill function is half working ? replacing the lower pixels with transparent but not the top?

